\begin{align*}
&\cos 5^\circ \cos 20^\circ + \cos 35^\circ \cos 50^\circ - \sin 5^\circ \sin 20^\circ - \sin 35^\circ \sin 50^\circ \\
&= \cos 5^\circ \cos 20^\circ - \sin 5^\circ \sin 20^\circ + \cos 35^\circ \cos 50^\circ - \sin 35^\circ \sin 50^\circ \\
&= \cos (5^\circ + 20^\circ) + \cos (35^\circ + 50^\circ) \\
&= \cos 25^\circ + \cos 85^\circ \\
&= \cos 25^\circ + \sin 5^\circ.
\end{align*}Similarly, we can write the denominator as
\begin{align*}
&\sin 5^\circ \cos 20^\circ - \sin 35^\circ \cos 50^\circ + \cos 5^\circ \sin 20^\circ - \cos 35^\circ \sin 50^\circ \\
&= \sin 5^\circ \cos 20^\circ + \cos 5^\circ \sin 20^\circ - \sin 35^\circ \cos 50^\circ - \cos 35^\circ \sin 50^\circ \\
&= \sin (5^\circ + 20^\circ) - \sin (35^\circ + 50^\circ) \\
&= \sin 25^\circ - \sin 85^\circ \\
&= \sin 25^\circ - \cos 5^\circ.
\end{align*}Therefore,
\[\tan \theta = \frac{\cos 25^\circ + \sin 5^\circ}{\sin 25^\circ - \cos 5^\circ}.\]Let $x = 5^\circ.$  Then
\begin{align*}
\tan \theta &= \frac{\cos 25^\circ + \sin 5^\circ}{\sin 25^\circ - \cos 5^\circ} \\
&= \frac{\cos (45^\circ - 20^\circ) + \sin 5^\circ}{\sin (45^\circ - 20^\circ) - \cos 5^\circ} \\
&= \frac{\cos 45^\circ \cos 20^\circ + \sin 45^\circ \sin 20^\circ + \sin 5^\circ}{\sin 45^\circ \cos 20^\circ - \cos 45^\circ \sin 20^\circ - \cos 5^\circ} \\
&= \frac{\cos (45^\circ - 20^\circ) + \sin 5^\circ}{\sin (45^\circ - 20^\circ) - \cos 5^\circ} \\
&= \tan (45^\circ - 20^\circ + 5^\circ) \\
&= \tan 30^\circ.
\end{align*}Thus, the minimum value of $\theta$ is $\boxed{30^\circ}.$

הנקודות $O,$ $A$ ו-$B$ מגדירות משולש $OAB.$

$\overrightarrow{OA} = \begin{pmatrix} 1 \\ 2 \\ 3 \end{pmatrix}$ ו-$\overrightarrow{OB} = \begin{pmatrix} -3 \\ -2 \\ 1 \end{pmatrix}$ מציינים את הנקודות $A$ ו-$B$ במרחב. מכאן, $\overrightarrow{AB} = \overrightarrow{OB} - \overrightarrow{OA} = \begin{pmatrix} -3 \\ -2 \\ 1 \end{pmatrix} - \begin{pmatrix} 1 \\ 2 \\ 3 \end{pmatrix} = \begin{pmatrix} -4 \\ -4 \\ -2 \end{pmatrix}.$

הנחנו ש-$\overrightarrow{OA} = \begin{pmatrix} 1 \\ 2 \\ 3 \end{pmatrix}$ ו-$\overrightarrow{OB} = \begin{pmatrix} -3 \\ -2 \\ 1 \end{pmatrix}.$

$\overrightarrow{OA} \times \overrightarrow{OB} = \begin{vmatrix} \mathbf{i} & \mathbf{j} & \mathbf{k} \\ 1 & 2 & 3 \\ -3 & -2 & 1 \end{vmatrix} = \mathbf{i}(2 \cdot 1 - 3 \cdot -2) - \mathbf{j}(1 \cdot 1 - 3 \cdot -3) + \mathbf{k}(1 \cdot -2 - 2 \cdot -3) = \begin{pmatrix} 8 \\ -10 \\ 4 \end{pmatrix}.$

$|\overrightarrow{OA} \times \overrightarrow{OB}| = \sqrt{8^2 + (-10)^2 + 4^2} = \sqrt{164} = 2 \sqrt{41}.$

$|\overrightarrow{AB}| = \sqrt{(-4)^2 + (-4)^2 + (-2)^2} = \sqrt{36} = 6.$

$[OAB] = \frac{1}{2} \cdot |\overrightarrow{OA} \times \overrightarrow{OB}| \cdot |\overrightarrow{AB}| = \frac{1}{2} \cdot 2 \sqrt{41} \cdot 6 = \boxed{6 \sqrt{41}}.$

The sum of the interior angles of an $n$-gon is $180(n-2)$ degrees.  The sum of the exterior angles of any polygon is $360$ degrees, so the sum of the interior and exterior angles of an $n$-gon is $180(n-2)+360=180n-360+360=180n$ degrees.  If we exclude one of the interior angles, the sum of the remaining angles is $180n-1070$ degrees.  Since the sum of the interior angles of an $n$-gon is $180n$ degrees, we have $180n-1070=180(n-2)$, so $180n-1070=180n-360$.  Solving for $n$, we find $n=\boxed{11}$.

ההector $\begin{pmatrix} 4 \\ -18 \\ -4 \end{pmatrix}$ שווה $2 \begin{pmatrix} 2 \\ -9 \\ -2 \end{pmatrix}$, hence the two lines are parallel.  We can find a point on the first line by setting $t = 0$, and we get the point $\begin{pmatrix} 3 \\ -10 \\ 1 \end{pmatrix}$.  We can find a point on the second line by setting $u = 0$, and we get the point $\begin{pmatrix} -5 \\ -3 \\ 6 \end{pmatrix}$.  The vector between these two points is
\[\begin{pmatrix} -5 \\ -3 \\ 6 \end{pmatrix} - \begin{pmatrix} 3 \\ -10 \\ 1 \end{pmatrix} = \begin{pmatrix} -8 \\ 7 \\ 5 \end{pmatrix}.\]The projection of this vector onto the direction vector of the lines is
\[\frac{\begin{pmatrix} -8 \\ 7 \\ 5 \end{pmatrix} \cdot \begin{pmatrix} 2 \\ -9 \\ -2 \end{pmatrix}}{\left\| \begin{pmatrix} 2 \\ -9 \\ -2 \end{pmatrix} \right\|^2} \begin{pmatrix} 2 \\ -9 \\ -2 \end{pmatrix} = \frac{1}{113} \begin{pmatrix} -8 \\ 7 \\ 5 \end{pmatrix}.\]The vector between the two lines is then
\[\begin{pmatrix} -8 \\ 7 \\ 5 \end{pmatrix} - \frac{1}{113} \begin{pmatrix} -8 \\ 7 \\ 5 \end{pmatrix} = \frac{112}{113} \begin{pmatrix} -8 \\ 7 \\ 5 \end{pmatrix}.\]The length of this vector is $\boxed{\frac{112}{\sqrt{113}}}$.

\begin{align*}
\sin (\alpha + \beta) &= \sin \alpha \cos \beta + \cos \alpha \sin \beta \\
&= 0.4 \sqrt{1 - 0.5^2} + \sqrt{1 - 0.4^2} \cdot 0.5 \\
&= 0.4 \cdot 0.86602540378 + 0.96 \cdot 0.5 \\
&= 0.34641016151 + 0.48 \\
&= 0.82641016151,
\end{align*}and
\begin{align*}
\sin (\alpha - \beta) &= \sin \alpha \cos \beta - \cos \alpha \sin \beta \\
&= 0.4 \sqrt{1 - 0.5^2} - \sqrt{1 - 0.4^2} \cdot 0.5 \\
&= 0.4 \cdot 0.86602540378 - 0.96 \cdot 0.5 \\
&= 0.34641016151 - 0.48 \\
&= -0.13358983849.
\end{align*}Therefore,
\[\sin (\alpha + \beta) \sin (\alpha - \beta) = 0.82641016151 \cdot (-0.13358983849) = \boxed{-0.1105572755}.\]

לפי נוסחת כפל המקדם, $x^3 + y^3 + z^3 - 3xyz = (x + y + z)(x^2 + y^2 + z^2 - xy - xz - yz).$ מכאן
\begin{align*}
(x + y + z)(x^2 + y^2 + z^2 - xy - xz - yz) &= 4 - 3 \cdot 4 \\
&= -8.
\end{align*} מכאן
\begin{align*}
(x + y + z)^2 &= x^2 + y^2 + z^2 + 2xy + 2xz + 2yz \\
&= (x^2 + y^2 + z^2 - xy - xz - yz) + 3(xy + xz + yz) \\
&= -8 + 3(xy + xz + yz).
\end{align*} מכאן
\begin{align*}
(x + y + z)^3 &= (x + y + z)(x + y + z)^2 \\
&= (x + y + z)(-8 + 3(xy + xz + yz)) \\
&= -8(x + y + z) + 3(xy + xz + yz)(x + y + z).
\end{align*} מכאן
\begin{align*}
(x + y + z)^3 + 8(x + y + z) &= 3(xy + xz + yz)(x + y + z) \\
&= 3(xy + xz + yz)(-8 + 3(xy + xz + yz)) \\
&= -24(xy + xz + yz) + 9(xy + xz + yz)^2.
\end{align*} מכאן
\begin{align*}
9(xy + xz + yz)^2 - 24(xy + xz + yz) - (x + y + z)^3 - 8(x + y + z) &= 0.
\end{align*} מכאן
\begin{align*}
9(xy + xz + yz)^2 - 24(xy + xz + yz) - (x + y + z)^3 - 8(x + y + z) &= 0 \\
\Rightarrow \quad 9(xy + xz + yz)^2 - 24(xy + xz + yz) - 64 &= 0 \\
\Rightarrow \quad (3(xy + xz + yz) - 8)(3(xy + xz + yz) + 8) &= 0.
\end{align*} מכאן $3(xy + xz + yz) - 8 = 0$ atau $3(xy + xz + yz) + 8 = 0.$

אם $3(xy + xz + yz) + 8 = 0,$ אז $xy + xz + yz = -\frac{8}{3}.$
